org.gvsig.raster.principalcomponents.swing

Interface PrincipalComponentsSwingManager

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultPrincipalComponentsSwingManager

    public interface PrincipalComponentsSwingManager
    This class is responsible of the management of the library's business logic. It is the library's main entry point, and provides all the services to manage PrincipalComponentsServices.
